FuncDef: The display configuration rollback changes load-result command displays the command that fails to be executed to load the configuration of the specified configuration rollback point and the failure cause.
ParentView: All views except the user view
Examples: Warning: The current operation may reduce the degree of account security. It is strongly recommended to keep this enabled.
ExtraInfo:
Usage Scenario
During the configuration rollback operation, some configurations may fail to be retrieved, and some configurations trigger the generation of prompt messages. You can run the display configuration rollback changes load-result command to view the command that fails to be executed and the failure cause.
